  "detailed_description": "Ducks in a Row is a sokoban style puzzle game where you navigate mazes in order to find all of your baby ducks. With over 50 levels ranging between parks, snowy landscapes, and even factories, there are sure to be diverse challenges on your way to reuniting Mama Duck with her babies. <br><br>While it may be cute, there are sure to be a few brain benders for those really seeking a challenge!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808260/extras/bb8be451555a9bce2c768b97401f6c95.apng?t=1724361908\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808260/extras/bb8be451555a9bce2c768b97401f6c95.poster.avif?t=1724361908\" class=\"bb_img\" width=320 height=64 /></picture></span>",
